title: [Solhaven, Tumbledown Lane]
description: A row of stone cottages lines the street, some washed in greens and blues.  A street peddler stands nearby, animatedly haggling with a dwarven woman over his wares.  Passersby simply walk around the pair, ignoring their animated discussion.

A row of stone cottages lines the street, some washed in greens and blues.  Clusters of gaudy jewels gleam beneath the garish awning of a street peddler's stall.  Nearby, a series of flagstone steps descend toward Bayside Road.
